Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.utils

Class TimeStampedMap<K,T>

java.lang.Object
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.utils.TimeStampedMap<K,T>
public class TimeStampedMap<K,T> extends Object
A Map that provides timestamped data obtained with a given retriever, which is used to fill in the data.
Author:
Thomas Pfau
